msgctxt "828"
msgid "Fashionable Hostess"
msgstr "Hostess a la moda"

msgctxt "832"
msgid "Talk_Quest"
msgstr "Talk_Quest"

msgctxt "836"
msgid "Stylish Hostess"
msgstr "Hostess con estilo"

msgctxt "840"
msgid "Talk_Yes"
msgstr "Talk_Yes"

msgctxt "84_Fashionable Hostess"
msgid "I think it's about time I got a new dress. Any suggestions?"
msgstr "Creo que ya es hora de que me compre un vestido nuevo. ¿Alguna recomendación?"

msgctxt "96_Stylish Hostess"
msgid "How about something in yellow? I don't think you have anything yellow."
msgstr "¿Qué tal algo amarillo? No creo que tengas nada amarillo."

msgctxt "108_Fashionable Hostess"
msgid "You're right. Plus, it's the perfect color for spring! Good thinking."
msgstr "Tienes razón. Además, ¡es el color perfecto para la primavera! Bien pensado."

msgctxt "120_Stylish Hostess"
msgid "I dunno if you'd call it \"good thinking.\" I just remembered how much you liked Indian curry..."
msgstr "No sé si esté bien pensado. Acabo de recordar lo mucho que te gustaba el curry indio..."

